data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home that effortlessly blends modern comfort with timeless appeal! As you approach, the large rocking chair front porch beckons you to relax and enjoy the tranquil surroundings. Step inside to discover the beauty of luxury vinyl plank flooring on the main areas downstairs, creating an elegant and low-maintenance living space. The bright and inviting entry sets the tone, leading you into a generously sized living area adorned with a cozy gas fireplace, which leads into the formal dining area, boasting beautiful french doors. The adjacent kitchen is a culinary delight, boasting stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a statement backsplash. A bright breakfast nook overlooks the lush back yard, creating a delightful space for your morning coffee. The primary suite, conveniently located on the main level, is a haven of tranquility. Enjoy the spaciousness and natural light, and retreat to the en suite bathroom featuring a double sink vanity, large garden tub, separate shower, and a walk-in closet that provides ample storage.Additional bedrooms are equally bright and spacious, offering comfortable living spaces for family or guests. The shared bathroom features a tub/shower combo, catering to both convenience and style. Step outside to the large fenced yard, where a patio area awaits - the perfect setting for entertaining guests or simply relaxing in the serene outdoors. This home is nestled in an established neighborhood, ensuring a sense of community and convenience. Experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and outdoor living in this meticulously maintained residence!
